            <div class="ingredient-item"><div class="ingredient-header"><span class="ingredient-name">Panthenol (Pro-Vitamin B5)</span><span class="ingredient-badge" style="background:rgba(45,74,64,0.08);color:var(--forest-2);">BARRIER SUPPORT</span></div><p class="ingredient-desc">Converts to pantothenic acid in the skin, where it supports cell repair and moisture retention. Particularly effective alongside barrier-repairing actives — it accelerates the recovery process and is a primary reason this serum is well-tolerated by sensitive skin types.</p></div>
            <div class="ingredient-item"><div class="ingredient-header"><span class="ingredient-name">Allantoin</span><span class="ingredient-badge" style="background:rgba(45,74,64,0.08);color:var(--forest-2);">SOOTHING</span></div><p class="ingredient-desc">A gentle keratolytic and soothing agent. Promotes controlled cell turnover, softens skin texture, and reduces sensitivity to actives. Contributes to the gradual improvement in tone and radiance most people notice by week three or four.</p></div>
          </div>
        {%- else -%}
          <p class="tab-para">Full ingredient list available on request. Contact us at Lalumecare@gmail.com.</p>
        {%- endif -%}
